name: Step Right Up
description: In preparation for my trip to Japan, I’d spent a LOT of time looking at satellite imagery, so there were a few things on my list which I’d only seen the roof of until I went and hunted them down.  At the top of that list was what appeared to be a hotel with scalloped balconies, but instead ended up being one giant mansion.  Fondly referred to as “my mansion,” this is what I stepped into.
